      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEKTRA BETA (2) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and four minors from 12 tries. Recorded a 1.3 lengths win (30.15) in a Grade 4 last time at The Meadows. Looks suited and should go close. TAKE A LITTLE (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at Angle Park following on from a second place finish (30.48) there the start prior. Has good speed and is aided by the cherry draw. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. COMPTON ROCKS (8) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at five of 17 starts including seven wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (29.87) over 512m at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has a good overall strike-rate and can find the frame here. GALENTO (3) comes off a (29.29) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a Grade 5 over 512m at this track. Has already won two times from this draw.",
